lead_paragraph: Dick Enberg spent many Midwestern nights and Saturday afternoons listening to baseball and football broadcasts on the radio. As soon as he could, he got behind a microphone himself.

headline.print_headline: Oh My! Enberg in Final Innings of Long Broadcasting Career
